{
  // A tree node (TreeNode — never "Node": that name is the ENGINE object-type marker, pre-set on every seeded node, which makes a so-named concept look already-cast on the first pass and silently skips its children) — a kernel Thought carrying its `depth` and (except the root) a `parent` ref. The
  // thought `text` is prose-terminal; the raw `score` (when the external judge wrote one) is snapped
  // by the kernel's Scored/Score::band — every gate downstream keys on the band, never the float.
  "require": ["Thought", "depth"]
}
